<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">Noam Chomsky: Trump Blaming WHO for COVID-19 Deaths Is Dictator-Like Behavior</h1>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<div class="row featured-media-block"><figure class="featured-media"><div class="mediawrapper"><iframe src="https://www.democracynow.org/embed/story/2020/4/17/noam_chomsky_coronavirus_trump_gaza_palestine" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe></div></figure></div>
<div class="row">
<div class="columns small-12 medium-4 sidebar-left">
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">By </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/amy-goodman/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Amy Goodman</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://www.democracynow.org/2020/4/17/noam_chomsky_coronavirus_trump_gaza_palestine' itemprop='url'>Democracy Now!</a></span></dd>
