<article class="row hentry post-270259 to4_video_post type-to4_video_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-interview tag-authoritarianism tag-covid-19 tag-donald-trump tag-noam-chomsky tag-world-health-organization section-politics-and-elections primary_topic-politics" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/OpinionNewsArticle">
<div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
<a class="archive-image" href="https://truthout.org/articles/trump-will-feed-you-to-covid-19-to-keep-the-money-happy/" title="Trump Will Feed You to COVID-19 to Keep the Money Happy">
<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0324-donald-trump-covid-19-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="President Trump gestures next to Response coordinator for White House Coronavirus Task Force Deborah Birx and Vice President Pence during the daily briefing on the novel coronavirus, COVID-19, at the White House, March 23, 2020, in Washington, D.C." loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0324-donald-trump-covid-19-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0324-donald-trump-covid-19-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0324-donald-trump-covid-19-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0324-donald-trump-covid-19-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0324-donald-trump-covid-19-2400x1800.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
</a>
</div>
<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns archive-text">
<div class="before-headline">
<div class='categories'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/category/op-ed/' rel='category' class='op-ed'>Op-Ed</a>
</div>
<div class='sections'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/section/environment-and-health/' rel='section' class='environment-and-health' style='color: #0ba864;'>Environment &amp; Health</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/trump-will-feed-you-to-covid-19-to-keep-the-money-happy/">Trump Will Feed You to COVID-19 to Keep the Money Happy</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">If Trump blows off the COVID-19 warnings, we the people must refuse to listen.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/william-rivers-pitt/" itemprop="url" rel="author">William Rivers Pitt</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://truthout.org' itemprop='url'>Truthout</a></span></dd>
</dl>
<time class="published updated meta-data" datetime="2020-03-24T14:53:39+00:00" itemprop="datePublished dateCreated" content="2020-03-24T14:53:39+00:00">March 24, 2020</time>
<div class="hide" itemprop="publisher" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization">
<a href="https://truthout.org" itemprop="url">
<span itemprop="name">
Truthout
</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
